example
  {property}{sides}-{size}
  {property}{sides}-{breakpoint}-{size}

  .mt-0 // margin top 0
  .ml-1 // margin left 1rem * 0.25
  .ml-lg-5 // 默认 991 以上尺寸，margin left = 1rem * 3



设置 margin/padding
  m - set margin
  p - set padding

设置属性
  t - margin-top or padding-top
  b - margin-bottom or padding-bottom
  l - margin-left or padding-left
  r - margin-right or padding-right
  x - set both *-left and *-right
  y - set both *-top and *-bottom

设置尺寸
  基于 system $spacer 设置尺寸
    0 - for classes that eliminate the margin or padding by setting it to 0
    1 - (by default) $spacer-x * .25 or $spacer-y * .25
    2 - (by default) $spacer-x * .5 or $spacer-y * .5
    3 - (by default) $spacer-x or $spacer-y
    4 - (by default) $spacer-x * 1.5 or $spacer-y * 1.5
    5 - (by default) $spacer-x * 3 or $spacer-y * 3

    * 默认 $spacer = 1rem

margin-auto
  针对固定宽度的 element，宽度居中
    <div class="mx-auto" style="width: 200px;">
      Centered element
    </div>








